# Security Policy

## Supported Versions
Only the latest version of this app is actively supported for security updates. 

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| 1.0.x   | :white_check_mark: |

## Reporting a Vulnerability
If you discover a security vulnerability or a major bug, please do not open a public issue. Instead, send a direct message via Reddit or open a private vulnerability report on GitHub. 

I will try to review and patch any critical issues within 48 hours.
